node.text:
We made these marmite chicken drumsticks with an air fryer on Sunday (24/5)
The chicken legs were first seasoned with marmite, salt , pepper and sesame oil and then placed in fridge overnight . Air fried the chicken at 200deg C for 30 mins. Turned the chicken after 15 mins.

The result- we were all happy with the end product, chicken tender and juicy!! Yummy 😋😋
.

#marmitechicken #airfriedmarmitechicken #circuitbreakersg #stayhomestaysafe #covid_19 #socialdistancing2020 #ahpekeats
@ahpekeats yes uncle!! Very satisfied! 🥳 thanks for cooking!
@meimei17 yes to prevent from sticking to the grill
Did you put the baking paper in the fryer?
